                            <comment id="189665" author="gerrit" created="Sun, 26 Mar 2017 06:48:46 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Oleg Drokin (oleg.drokin@intel.com) merged in patch &lt;a href=&quot;https://review.whamcloud.com/26022/&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://review.whamcloud.com/26022/&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br/&gt;
Subject: &lt;a href=&quot;https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-9216&quot; title=&quot;Interop: 2.7.0 client fails to mount on  ~2.9.53 server&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;LU-9216&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;LU-9216&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt; config: move config types into lustre_idl.h&lt;br/&gt;
